Figs 
1, 2

), distal margin of female sternite VII with (
4
) more slender, posteriorly produced lateral margins and with (
5
) narrow median concavity more inwardly produced (

Figs 
12

, 
19
), and (
6
) anterior margin of bases of first valvulae in ventral view broadly concave (

